Apply the following vscode settings for valid dsljs experience:
    Associate dsl.js files to javascript linting and intelisense;
    Enable semantic highlighting
    and
    Disable js validations. Otherwise you will get lsp erros. Uneeded for this type of macro based programming
     
```json
    "files.associations": {
        "*.dsl.js": "javascript"
    },
    "[javascript]": {
        "editor.semanticHighlighting.enabled": true
    },
    "javascript.validate.enable": false,
```